title: #86: God (Steve Simeone, Steve Rannazzisi, Jesus)
itunes:title: God with Steve Simeone, Steve Rannazzisi, Jesus
description: Steve Rannazzisi and Steve Simeone came over to my abortion of an apartment to talk a little about faith. Each of us is in a pretty different place in terms of belieif. Simeone goes to church every Sunday, Rannazzisi is in this in between place where he doesn't pray but he does the ritual things, and I am the only one who believes in logic and provable things. It was a good discussion, I wish it had gone longer.
